name: Dig
overview: When FBI Agent Peter Connelly, recently stationed in Jerusalem, begins investigating the murder of a young American, he realizes that he’s uncovered an ancient international conspiracy that threatens to change the course of human history. Certain that the dangerous prophecy is nearing fruition, Peter must race against the clock to unravel its mystery. From a remote farm in Norway, to an enigmatic compound in New Mexico, to the serpentine tunnels of Jerusalem, he searches for the truth, the revelation of which will shake the world's beliefs to its very core.
tagline: The deeper you dig, the further you get from the truth.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: In the premiere, FBI agent Peter Donnelly unearths an international mystery while investigating the murder of a young American in Jerusalem.

episodes.name: Catch You Later
episodes.overview: Peter searches for the murderer while also pursuing Yussef Khalid and forms an uneasy alliance with Det. Golan Cohen while dealing with an unexpected revelation. Avram begins his journey to Israel with the red heifer and Billingham and his disciplines prepare Josh for a life-changing event.

episodes.name: Meet the Rosenbergs
episodes.overview: Peter's pursuit of Khalid dead ends and he and Cohen follow clues found in Emma's journal. Debbie takes Josh for an unauthorized outing and Avram continues his journey to Jerusalem.

episodes.name: Prayer of David
episodes.overview: Peter's discovery of an ancient coded secret leads to a race to find the final stone. Debbie faces the consequences for her attempted kidnapping of Josh. Avram is shadowed by a deadly assassin.

episodes.name: Emma Wilson's Father
episodes.overview: Peter delves into Emma's past, which leads to the discovery of a long-hidden, ancient symbol; someone from Debbie's past attempts to rescue her; and Lynn's life is put in jeopardy.

episodes.name: The Well of Souls
episodes.overview: Cohen arrests Emma's suspected killer; Peter makes a startling discovery; Avram and the red heifer are kidnapped in Croatia; and Billingham tries to prevent Debbie and Josh from exposing his secrets.

episodes.name: Trust No One
episodes.overview: After a startling breakthrough on the case, Peter turns to Golan for new clues; Ridell pressures Lynn to get Peter out of the country; Debbie must trade with Tad Billingham; Rabbi Lev and a partner work in the underground tunnels.

episodes.name: Sisters of Dinah
episodes.overview: Lynn suspects that there may be a mole at the consulate; Margrove and Peter both head to a convent, but they have different goals; and Debbie returns to the compound seeking vengeance.

episodes.name: Jehoshaphat
episodes.overview: An ancient religious sect is ready to enact its plan; Peter partners with unlikely allies; Lynn realizes the depth of the conspiracy while investigating Ridell; Golan tries to crack more clues from the Donaldson case; and Avram moves to protect his valuable asset.

episodes.name: Armageddon Protocol
episodes.overview: Peter races to stop the Order of Moriah's plans of destroying the Temple Mount.
